    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 4.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第4课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "An Exciting Trip.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "激动人心的旅行。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Why is Tim finding this trip exciting?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "为什么蒂姆觉得这次旅行令人兴奋？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "I have just received a letter from my brother, Tim.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我刚刚收到弟弟蒂姆的一封信。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "He is in Australia.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他正在澳大利亚。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "He has been there for six months.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他在那里已经待了六个月。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "Tim is an engineer.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "蒂姆是一名工程师。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "He is working for a big firm and he has already visited a great number of different places in Australia.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他在一家大公司工作，并且已经去过澳大利亚许多不同的地方。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "He has just bought an Australian car and has gone to Alice Springs, a small town in the center of Australia.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他刚买了一辆澳大利亚汽车，现在已经去了澳大利亚中部的小镇艾丽斯斯普林斯。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "He will soon visit Darwin.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他不久还将到达尔文去。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "From there, he will fly to Perth.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "从那里，他将飞往珀斯。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "My brother has never been abroad before, so he is finding this trip very exciting.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我弟弟以前从未出过国，因此他觉得这次旅行非常令人兴奋。"
      }
    }
  ],
